main event: In November 1964, multiple unidentified flying objects were reported in Carmichaels, Pennsylvania.
interesting points: The conclusion of the report is categorized as CHAP., The report references materials that were determined to penetrate radar defense., Major Quintanilla, Jr. acknowledged the sighting in a letter dated 1 Jan 1965., There were several sightings reported starting in 1964., An interest in the phenomenon is expressed in a letter dated Jan 26, 1965.
